---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Disclaimer from '../components/Disclaimer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About Antonio Rodríguez Martínez"
	description="Systems builder. Warrior poet. Father. I write, build, and create with integrity."
	pubDate={new Date('May 01 2025')}
	language={['en']}
	category={['about']}
	robots={{
		index: true,
		follow: true,
		noarchive: false,
		nosnippet: false,
		noimageindex: false
	}}
	layoutType="blog"
>
	<div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
		<p class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">
			I build systems — digital, emotional, spiritual, and physical.
		</p>

		<p class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">
			I'm a technical program manager, software architect, and developer with over a decade of experience building scalable products. I've founded companies, led teams, and shipped software used by millions. Now I split my time between building tools, raising my kids, and building a homestead in Puerto Rico.
		</p>

		<p class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">
			But that's just part of it.
		</p>

		<p class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">
			I'm also a father, artist, martial artist, mentor, and the founder of <strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">Strong Hands, Soft Heart</strong> — a brand devoted to practical strength, emotional depth, and sacred self-reliance.
		</p>

		<p class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">
			This blog is where I document it all:
		</p>

		<ul class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">Art & Expression</strong> 🎵 — creative soul, aesthetic power, truth-telling</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">DIY & Creation</strong> 🛠️ — physical builds, handmade goods, crafting</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">Integration & Growth</strong> 🧘🏽‍♂️ — inner mastery, parenting, masculine leadership</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">Learning Projects</strong> 📚 — documentation of mastery in progress</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">Metaspace</strong> 🌀 — reflections on the journey itself</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">Parenting</strong> 👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 — raising resilient children, family dynamics, and personal growth</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">Politics</strong> ⚖️ — power dynamics, social structures, and collective healing</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">Psychology</strong> 🧠 — human behavior, social dynamics, and mental processes</li>
			<li><strong class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">Systems & Strategy</strong> 💻 — technical systems, organizational design, and strategic thinking</li>
		</ul>

		<p class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">
			Join me on this journey of exploration, creation, and growth.
		</p>

		<h2 class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">👇 Links</h2>
		<ul class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">
			<li>🛠 <a href="https://builds.software" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-500 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">Builds.software</a> — my technical portfolio</li>
			<li>💜 <a href="https://stronghandssoftheart.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-500 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">Strong Hands, Soft Heart</a> — my brand</li>
			<li>🐙 <a href="https://github.com/antoniwan" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-500 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">GitHub</a> — open source & code</li>
			<li>🌀 <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/antoniwan.online" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-500 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">BlueSky</a> — my social brain</li>
		</ul>

		<p class="text-text dark:text-text-dark">
			If you're building something good, or trying to become someone better,<br />
			I'm probably down to help.<br />
			Get in touch.
		</p>

		<Disclaimer />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	/* Smooth transitions for dark mode */
	.prose {
		transition: color 300ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
	}

	/* Respect reduced motion preferences */
	@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
		.prose {
			transition: none !important;
		}
	}
</style>

